<A>__{he bends to pet the old dog goodbye... he takes up his suitcase and starts off the porch... going down the walkway... he hesitates, and opens the gate... moving out onto the street... when suddenly daisy is calling him...}
<C>__{daisy}
<D>__{benjamin... benjamin...}
<A>__{she comes running. he stops to let her catch up to him...}
<C>__{daisy }
<D>__{where are you going?}
